    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Does that mean that the header and footer templates are still defined within the widget, but they get placed outside of the widget? Example isn't totally clear\r\n\r\nThe example is actually wrong, sorry for that.\r\n\r\nThe usage is the same as before. You pass the template using a single parameters object, and then internally each layer pick the options they need.",
