    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Discussed about that in team meeting:\r\n - let's stick with the options that are merged together as it is closer to the current API\r\n - the rendering out of the lifecycle is not crazy good but we don't have a better option for now\r\n - we agreed to move forward (and subsequently update the RFC)\r\n\r\nLet me know if I deformed what we said @algolia/instantsearch-for-websites :)",
